description.narrative: 3.2 Additional Households, in 685 peri-urban and rural communities, have knowledge and able to alleviate harmful hygiene and sanitation practices and norms that impact on their health, which contributes to Hygiene, Sanitation. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: More communities use sustained WASH services and are empowered to stop harmful sanitation and hygiene behaviours.
